                <p style="font-weight:bold;">Baby sitters rate - £10/hr (minimum 4 hrs booking required)</p>

                <p style="font-weight:bold;">Bank holiday rates - £12 - 15/hr (minimum of 4 hrs booking required)</p>

                <p>Agency fee for a one off booking is £30 with no additional booking charges. <a href="/services/EmergencyChildcare" style="text-decoration:underline;">Click here</a> for more information on emergency childcare/one off bookings.</p>

                <p><a href="/home/contact" style="text-decoration:underline;">Contact us</a> to book your first babysitting service through us. Rest assured, we will not let you down.</p>
                
